{"tid":1960786,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國海軍戰爭學院國際法中心主任：美國可以註銷中国持有的美債、將中国逐出世貿","createTime":"2020-04-06T11:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T05:33:28.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc02d77a538453315b9fc3760398974eb8e8f1dc","tid":1960786,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"美國海軍戰爭學院國際法中心主任 James Kraska 指出，中国政府因並未迅速及透明地分享武漢肺炎疫情資訊，導致疫症在世界各地大爆發，已違反世衛的國際衛生條例（2005）。根據國際法當中《關於國家不法行為責任的條款》，如果中国政府被國際法庭裁定需要賠償而中方拒絕的話，受害國可以採取的行動包括：美國可以註銷中国持有的美債、將中国逐出世貿，甚至可以包括一般被視為違反國際法或侵害主權國家的行動；也就是說幾乎沒有甚麼限制。<br />\n<br />\nCHINA IS LEGALLY RESPONSIBLE FOR COVID-19 DAMAGE AND CLAIMS COULD BE IN THE TRILLIONS<br />\n<a href=\"https://warontherocks.com/2020/03/china-is-legally-responsible-for-covid-19-damage-and-claims-could-be-in-the-trillions/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwarontherocks.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fchina-is-legally-responsible-for-covid-19-damage-and-claims-could-be-in-the-trillions%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLcwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=c813586d\" target=\"_blank\">https://warontherocks.com/2020/03/china-is-legally-responsible-for-covid-19-damage-and-claims-could-be-in-the-trillions/</a>"},{"pid":"3e13260507d8eea940a8f2aa47493c454b140f89","tid":1960786,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"咁愛滋病可唔可以告番美國"},{"pid":"3555c5228fc3f7245a7df1968d349075bd29379f","tid":1960786,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e13260507d8eea940a8f2aa47493c454b140f89","tid":1960786,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"咁愛滋病可唔可以告番美國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"中国政府因並未迅速及透明地分享武漢肺炎疫情資訊，導致疫症在世界各地大爆發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8722cebfb7e3a76ad17fd97fed7bcdff6bcf57d","tid":1960786,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy